# ⚠️  This file is OUTDATED and kept only for historical reference.
#
# The project now uses per-package env files:
#   backend/.env.example   → Backend (FastAPI + Supabase + Neo4j + LLM)
#   frontend/.env.example  → Frontend (Vite + Supabase)
#
# Setup instructions:
#   1. cp backend/.env.example backend/.env  → fill in your backend values
#   2. cp frontend/.env.example frontend/.env → fill in your frontend values
#
# DO NOT copy this file. Use the per-package examples above instead.
